App Name: Beati Cafe

Description: Beati Cafe is a modern, cozy, and welcoming cafe that offers a curated selection of specialty coffee, teas, and freshly baked pastries. The cafe focuses on providing a warm and relaxing environment where customers can enjoy quality beverages and light meals, whether they are working, meeting friends, or simply taking a break.

The brand emphasizes simplicity, comfort, and quality, with a visually appealing aesthetic that combines modern minimalism with cozy, earthy elements. Beati Cafe wants its digital presence to reflect its physical ambiance: inviting, professional, and easy to navigate.

The target audience includes young professionals, students, and coffee enthusiasts who appreciate quality drinks, a pleasant atmosphere, and an effortless user experience online and offline.
